No. 11-678 (R46-006). Central States, Southeast and Southwest Areas Health and Welfare Fund, Petitioner v. Bio-Medical Application of Tennessee, Inc. 565 U.S. 1152, 132 S. Ct. 1087,

181 L. Ed. 2d 805,

2012 U.S. LEXIS 580. January 11, 2012.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46.1 of the Rules of this Court.

Same case below, 656 F.3d 277.
